<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0148001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148001">當為印度曆之第二月。</note>
<note n="0148002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148002">作三十名友人之童子等一團體稱跋陀羅〔善賢〕組。</note>
<note n="0148003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148003">有優樓頻羅、那提、伽耶之三兄弟迦葉導一千之結鬘行者。</note>
<note n="0148004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148004">印度曆之第一月。</note>
<note n="0148005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148005">今之錫蘭島。</note>
<note n="0150006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0150006">協會本為鬱達求羅波耶。</note>
<note n="0150007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0150007">印度曆之第一月。</note>
<note n="0151008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0151008">註為水生類、陸生類、及為龍蛇之類。</note>
<note n="0152009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0152009">或為高價。</note>
<note n="0153010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0153010">以下總就現在而言。即今之摩訶眉伽林園所立之意。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
